{"tid":1495643,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"話說有冇人撘荃灣線個陣feel到對眼有d辣？","createTime":"2019-08-22T06:58:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T10:10:53.000Z","uid":186908,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"490fc26f599c97f143e7e18c7e4e45fdbe1afc43","tid":1495643,"uid":186908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T06:58:53.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相隔左班狗射催淚彈一段時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n我琴日撘荃灣線嗰陣企係近車門嗰啲位，就feel到對眼有啲「那」。我由開始上車到落車係咁標眼水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，甚至聞到少少味有反胃既感覺。<br />\n本身都冇為意，但係近幾次只要企喺風口位就會咁。有次見個外傭係咁卒眼，佢又係咁標眼水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知關唔關事<br />\n同一情況下係上次馬鞍山天橋射咗催淚彈附近，我都有同樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n特登開post問吓有冇人有同樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Btw有冇得投訴？<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"c760e6b33005b2d626cc4207c860b03f50717ffc","tid":1495643,"uid":186908,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T06:59:27.000Z","msg":"討論下 有冇人有相同情況？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea979f2444624d9e77e7ee67013ba7b5f89ca50","tid":1495643,"uid":186908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T07:00:20.000Z","msg":"召喚撘荃灣線嘅巴絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a801d57c0066499e0214ef4dbb8b041a92359302","tid":1495643,"uid":5475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T07:01:24.000Z","msg":"嘴唇會feel 到 那那地"},{"pid":"ec2e7b99f389f52f7d76f5da8ebd4a5a485b748c","tid":1495643,"uid":8175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T07:02:37.000Z","msg":"馬鞍山天橋果粒唔係胡椒彈咩"},{"pid":"9ef45ae2529814c9542916f862a696f29aadf045","tid":1495643,"uid":186908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec2e7b99f389f52f7d76f5da